Maintainer: Sokolova Maria <kyashinura@yandex.ru>
Description:
    Provides utilities for analysing GitHub profiles, collecting commit and
    repository metadata, loading analytical tables into ClickHouse, scanning
    dependency snapshots with Syft and the OSV database, and asking
    OpenAI-compatible models questions over ClickHouse data through local
    tool-calling helpers.
